## Stylesheets

### Stylesheets
* Linking a CSS
* CSS Syntax
* Text Properties


### CSS Rule Set
CSS syntax

```css
selector {
    property: value;   /* one rule */
    property: value;
}

```


### CSS Rule Set
Example Rule Set

```css
h1 {
    font-family: serif;
    font-size: 120%;
}
```


### Hooking up CSS
Link the Stylesheet to each HTML page

```html
<head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
```


### CSS Properties
CSS Property Groups

* Text
* Color
* Spacing
* Borders


